title: Game Developer ( Mobile HTML5 / Web / Multiplayer / Programmer )
additional_title:
Beberapa lokasi kerja
IDR 4.000.000 - IDR 8.000.000
Ditayangkan pada 9-Oct-23
job_desc:
We are hiring remote HTML5 game developers from all parts of Indonesia. If you have real experience building HTML5 games or applications, you're highly encouraged to apply.
Very important notes:
- In your application, please send samples of your past HTML5 related projects. We evaluate all projects very seriously.
- If you have experience doing HTML5 multiplayer or HTML5 3D games, this is a plus point.
- We are only hiring technical game programmers. If you are a sales/product manager/someone of a very senior rank, please do not apply.
- Please apply in English only
Responsibilities:
1) The ideal candidate shall build web and mobile games using cutting edge HTML5 technology.
2) Responsible for developing web and mobile application.
3) To provide maintenance and support of application development.
The candidate should know:
1) responsive web design,
2) how to build lightweight mobile front end applications
3) understand the challenges of designing on the native browsers of Android, iOS and also Desktop browsers (IE, Chrome, Firefox)
Most importantly, we're looking for candidates who fit our company culture, are fast learners, and extremely motivated. Everything else is secondary.
Core requirements:
1) Must have experience in building games, either as school projects or hobby
2) Experience at HTML, HTML5, Javascript and CSS
3) Has built 2D, 3D or multiplayer HTML5 games before, either as side project or real project
4) Strong programming skills. Able to learn new programming languages quickly.
5) Experience developing web apps on mobile devices
6) Ability to communicate in spoken and written English
7) Ability to work independently, in small teams
8) Keen attention to detail, impeccable sense of design. Able to write structured code.
9) Degree or Diploma in Internet/Web Design/Computer Science/Engineering/Multimedia Technology or any related field. If you're from an outside field, but would like to try, we welcome it too.
Bonus points for:
1) Ability to communicate in another foreign language
2) Experience working at a web/digital agency
3) Experience with server side languages
4) Experience working on real HTML5 game projects
5) Knowledge of programming in server side languages (Python/PHP/Ruby).
In your application, please send samples of your past HTML5 related projects or backend systems/applications that you have built. We evaluate all projects very seriously.

title: Expert Data Scientist
job_desc:
Tanggung Jawab Utama:
Menganalisis data dengan menggunakan teknik-teknik analisis statistik dan machine learning untuk mengidentifikasi tren, pola, dan wawasan bisnis yang relevan.
Mengembangkan model prediksi dan algoritma yang canggih untuk meramalkan perilaku pelanggan, permintaan pasar, dan kinerja produk.
Mengolah dan membersihkan data dari berbagai sumber untuk memastikan kualitas dan keakuratan data yang digunakan dalam analisis.
Berkolaborasi dengan tim lintas disiplin untuk mengidentifikasi tantangan bisnis dan mengusulkan solusi berdasarkan analisis data.
Menerapkan metode visualisasi data yang efektif untuk menyajikan wawasan secara jelas kepada pemangku kepentingan.
Kemampuan yang dibutuhkan:
S1/S2 di bidang Ilmu Komputer, Statistik, Matematika, atau bidang yang relevan.
Pengalaman dalam menerapkan teknik analisis data dan machine learning untuk memecahkan masalah bisnis yang kompleks.
Kemampuan dalam menggunakan bahasa pemrograman seperti Python atau R untuk analisis data dan pengembangan model.
Pengalaman dengan alat-alat analisis data seperti pandas, NumPy, scikit-learn, atau alat-alat sejenis.
Pengetahuan tentang teknik visualisasi data dan alat-alat seperti Matplotlib, Seaborn, atau alat visualisasi lainnya.
Kemampuan komunikasi yang baik untuk menyajikan temuan kompleks secara jelas kepada audiens non-teknis.
Keahlian dalam pengolahan dan analisis big data akan menjadi nilai tambah.
Memiliki pengalaman minimal 3 tahun dibidang data science.

title: Software Developer - API Integration Specialist
job_desc:
Position Overview: 
We are seeking a highly skilled Software Developer with extensive expertise in API-first development frameworks and a deep understanding of API integrations, food delivery APIs. The ideal candidate will play a pivotal role in designing, developing, and maintaining seamless API integrations that enhance platform functionality and user experience. If you are passionate about creating innovative solutions and have a strong background in API-driven development, we invite you to join our dynamic team. 
Key Responsibilities: 
API Integration and Development: Design, develop, and maintain API integrations to connect platforms with external APIs, including Shopify, Uber Eats, Zomato, and Swiggy food delivery services. 
API-first Development: Champion API-first development methodologies, ensuring that APIs are well-documented, scalable, and follow best practices to support current and future needs. 
Technical Expertise: Leverage your extensive knowledge of API development frameworks to create efficient and reliable integrations that meet business requirements and adhere to industry standards. 
Platform Enhancements: Collaborate with cross-functional teams to identify opportunities for API-driven enhancements to our platform. Develop new features and functionalities that enhance user experience and drive business growth. 
Code Quality and Testing: Write clean, maintainable code and conduct thorough testing to ensure the performance, security, and reliability of API integrations. Implement debugging and troubleshooting when necessary. 
Performance Optimisation: Optimise API performance, responsiveness, and data retrieval to ensure seamless and lightning-fast user experiences. 
Third-party API Management: Manage and monitor third-party API integrations, addressing issues, maintaining documentation, and staying updated with changes and updates from API providers. 
Collaboration and Communication: Work closely with designers, product managers, and other developers to align API integrations with overall project goals and timelines. Communicate effectively to gather requirements, provide updates, and address technical challenges. 
Qualifications and Experience: 
Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering, or related field. 
Proven experience as a Software Developer with a strong focus on API-first development and API integrations. 
Extensive knowledge of API development frameworks and best practices. 
Expertise in working with Shopify API, as well as Uber Eats, Zomato, and Swiggy food delivery APIs. 
Proficiency in programming languages such as Python, Node.js, or others relevant to API development. 
Experience with version control systems (e.g., Git), API documentation tools, and testing frameworks. 
Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail. 
Excellent communication and teamwork abilities. 
Portfolio showcasing API integration projects and technical capabilities. 
Additional Information: 
This is a full-time position based at our Bandung/Bali office. 
Use of the latest Agile Frameworks
Opportunities to work on Large and Small Projects
Collaboration with Multinational Teams
Employee Benefits Schemes 
Flexible and Co-operative Work Culture
Excellent Work-Life Balance
Competitive Salary and BPJS
Private and Group Corporate English Courses

title: RnD Senior Software Engineer - Machine Vision
additional_title:
Beberapa lokasi kerja
IDR 15.000.000 - IDR 30.000.000
Ditayangkan pada 14-Sep-23
job_desc:
Headquartered in Dubai, United Arab Emirates, FORMULATRIX is a fast-growing robotic automation equipment manufacturer and software solutions provider to leading pharmaceutical companies and academic research institutions including major Fortune 500 and Fortune 100 companies. The company has aggressively grown because of our industry-recognized patented technology and superior software delivery services.
We are seeking a hands-on, top-notch Senior Software Engineer with a Machine Vision specialization. In this role, you'll be responsible for designing and developing software solutions for machine vision systems.
Job Description:
Design, develop, and improve robotic/machine vision systems software from the ground up.
Use research and development skills to create prototypes that solve challenging problems in machine vision and machine control.
Analyze challenges and propose options and timelines for resolving those challenges.
Collaborate with a global team of peers in software engineering, as well as those on the mechanical and electrical side, and implement solutions in a timely manner.
Provide our customers with great support and intuitive applications that turn complex engineering solutions into a simple user experience.
Stay abreast of new technologies in your field and adapt as needed.
Requirements:
Candidates must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, Electronic Engineering, or equivalent professional experience in machine vision software development.
Have at least 2 years of experience in machine vision development, delivery, and post-implementation. Please showcase this in your resume and highlight the technology stack used.
Demonstrate good experience and best practice programming in C / C++ / C# / Java. Good fundamentals in OOP/OOAD are an advantage.
Demonstrate strong fundamentals in computer science: model-driven development, algorithms, and others.
Be committed to writing good quality and high-performance code in a limited resources machine (i.e. SingleBoard Computer).
Demonstrate good logical thinking as well as attention to detail.
Have a passion to build great solutions and impress both colleagues and customers.
Have a "Can Do" attitude and take pride in what you do.
Be proactive, highly motivated, and a strong team player with a good ability to multi-task and re-prioritize as necessary.
Possess good communication skills in English both oral and written.
Applicants must be willing to work in either Salatiga, Semarang, or Bandung.
